            <abstract>
                <p>This short version of the homiliary dedicated to the Saviour of the World and his feast contains names Brigitte (ብረዜዳ፡), Matilda (ሜቴልዳ፡), and Elizabeth (ኤልሳቤጥ፡). This was later condensed and revised into a short prayer usually appended to MSS of ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡ which simply begins "ዜና፡ ሕማማቲሁ፡ ለክርስቶስ፡" and names Mary Magdalene, Salome, and Elizabeth.</p>
            </abstract>
